title: [Noralgar Hollow, Moonlight Pool]
description: The trail veers close to the bank of the lake, drawn by a spectacular view of the falls just across a narrow arm of Moonlight Pool.  A few carved stone benches are positioned along the bank, offering a place to sit and regard the beautiful cascade.

The trail veers close to the bank of the lake, drawn by a spectacular view of the falls just across a narrow arm of Moonlight Pool.  A few carved stone benches are positioned along the bank, offering a place to sit and regard the beautiful cascade.  A couple of cabins are built on the path's eastern shoulder, their view of the lake unencumbered.
